reviewText: I would have liked it more if it was a DVD, but I didn't pay attention when I ordered it.  The music is good  but you have to already know the moves or its just a waste of time.  Next time I will read what I'm buying.  Once I saw that it was just music I didn't use it.  It was my own fault!
I LOVE this CD.  I use it every day for my clients and it is nice to have this in my music library.

I absolutely love it!!!
I play it all the time on my commute.
